Hm. This sounds a lot like questions for good research paper. You
should probably start by reading some articles on the subject and, if
you have time, playing around with JUnit a little. Try
http://www.junit.org. You might even try the excellent JUnit: A Starter
Guide and JUnit: A Primer, which describe JUnit from the beginning.

Best of luck.
